responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "0F37AAA8420DE7FFD942C396B982DCA8", "The Terrorgore Minotaur are usually a wandering group, they\'re not even native to the Riverlands originally. This is the first time I\'ve seen them poking around old Oakenbane, though, they usually stick to the open plains.")
